One dead and three others sustained injuries following a head on collision involving two vehicle&#8217;s on the R513 in Hartebeespoort on Tuesday. According to Netcare911 paramedics the incident happened at about 07:00am. Netcare911 spokesperson Athlenda Mathe said that detail to the cause of the accident still remain a subject for police investigation and comment. The Netcare2 helicopter was then dispatched to the scene to airlift a critically injured man to a level 1 trauma facility in Johannesburg for further medical care, said Mathe. All injured patients were transported to hospitals in North West.&nbsp;-TNA Reporter 